<p>Cubby House Bunk Bed with Open Shelves - Model LFTCBBYOS</p>

<p>High Loft Bed with Open Shelves &amp; Optional 2 Drawer Desk - Model LFTWDSK</p>

<p>Triple Bunk Bed - Single Over Double Bed plus Optional Trundle - Model BNKTP2</p>

<p>Triple Transverse Bunk Bed - Three Single Beds in One - Model BNKTP1</p>
